text:
A general view southeastward from the Woodside station of the Interborough and B.M.T. Subway Lines (elevated here) located at 61st Street and Queens Boulevard, showing in the center background the Penn Manufacturing Company also known as the Woodside Brewery.

May 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
